      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ciclo di report-program                 *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   prn-rou-pri-000      thru prn-rou-pri-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-pgm-frg-600.
       exe-pgm-frg-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se sort eseguito                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Continuazione                           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-pgm-frg-600.
       exe-pgm-frg-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
